Package nl.vpro.web.filter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExclusionStrategy  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DummyExclusionStrategy
    dummy implementation that passes all requests
    ExpireHeadersFilter
    Make sure that all pages will expire in 5 minutes.
    ResponseHeaderFilter
    Filter to set headers on all matching requests, the following example sets headers to avoid caching:

    PrivateResponseHeaderFilter nl.vpro.dvt.communities.web.ResponseHeaderFilter Cache-Control private,no-cache,no-store Pragma no-cache

    RootOnlyStrategy
    This exclusion strategy is a workaround for an issue with a filter being mapped to "/" did not work.
    SplashPageFilter
    Determines whether or not a splash page should be shown.
    SwfAttachmentFilter
    http://www.adobe.com/devnet/flashplayer/articles/ fplayer10_security_changes_02.html#head32 describes a change in the flash player that ignores any flash content that is served with a Content-Disposition header with the value 'attachment'.
